Row 3: Debt & Returns
Card 1: Total Debt
Large number (selected currency)
Breakdown: Short-term vs Long-term (click to expand)
Card 2: Next Loan Payment
Amount (in loan currency or selected currency)
Due date with countdown (e.g., "Due in 7 days")
Loan name
Card 3: Debt-to-Equity Ratio
Number (e.g., 1.5)
Color indicator:
Green: <1 (low debt)
Yellow: 1-2 (moderate)
Red: >2 (high debt)
Card 4: Interest Coverage Ratio
Number (EBIT / Interest Expense)
Color indicator (Green >3, Yellow 1.5-3, Red <1.5)
Card 5: ROE (Return on Equity)
Percentage
Color indicator (Green >15%, Yellow 10-15%, Red <10%)
Trend sparkline
Card 6: ROA (Return on Assets)
Percentage
Color indicator (Green >10%, Yellow 5-10%, Red <5%)
Trend sparkline
Card 7: ROI (Return on Investment)
Percentage (overall business ROI or specific campaign ROI)
Color indicator
Trend sparkline
Row 4: Operational Metrics
Card 1: Average CAC (Customer Acquisition Cost)
Amount (selected currency)
Trend indicator
Target comparison (if set)
Card 2: Average CLTV (Customer Lifetime Value)
Amount (selected currency)
Trend indicator
CLTV/CAC ratio displayed
Card 3: Average ROAS (Return on Ad Spend)
Multiplier (e.g., 3.5x)
Color indicator (Green >3x, Yellow 2-3x, Red <2x)
Trend indicator
Card 4: Inventory Turnover
Number (e.g., 6x)
Times per year
Industry benchmark comparison (if available)
Card 5: Cash Cycle
Days (e.g., 85 days)
Trend indicator
Target comparison (e.g., "15 days above target")
Card 6: Working Capital
Amount (selected currency)
Trend indicator
Current ratio displayed
